 combines the collagen-inducing benefits of traditiona...","url":"https://www.eyre-esthetics.com/post/what-is-rf-microneedling","title":"What Is RF Microneedling & Skin Benefits Explained","encrypted_index":"Eo8BCioIEBgCIiQ3ZWM1ZDE4ZC04YThiLTQ5OTItOTY1Zi05YWEwN2RhYThhY2ESDDIF8WYwE+E9fh8dBxoM1OC1knIn+dOxFiQ+IjBc/ZAqQf5wMWXCb6HSDLn5FRHqGlB2HBNOeTB9NQoaOrQJS7rudYpKWUufI5YTP+4qExuu4BZsOaMeqBk9bZPZhtGahzMYBA=="}],"type":"text","text":"Radiofrequency microneedling is an advanced, minimally invasive skin rejuvenation treatment that combines the collagen-inducing benefits of traditional microneedling with the deep tissue remodeling effects of RF energy."},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n---\n\n### How It Works\n\n"},{"citations":[{"type":"web_search_result_location","cited_text":"The process involves using a device with fine needles to create micro-injuries in the skin, similar to traditional microneedling. However, RF micronee...","url":"https://santeclinics.com/blog/radiofrequency-microneedling-differences","title":"RF Microneedling: Benefits and Differences Explained.","encrypted_index":"EpEBCioIEBgCIiQ3ZWM1ZDE4ZC04YThiLTQ5OTItOTY1Zi05YWEwN2RhYThhY2ESDEgvKWNsRrpDz9BuvBoMrZw1AS6w1efJtx/JIjBjl5Nl6GAmbjiRC7uZuB4hJJd4joAKuEj91lHdi2laxbkRcuZJrSm+Qa1NL3QHx+EqFVofU6iIrgL5x2KJNaLBYp8yIZJ+chgE"}],"type":"text","text":"The process involves using a device with fine needles to create micro-injuries in the skin, similar to traditional microneedling. However, RF microneedling devices also emit radiofrequency energy into the deeper layers of the skin through these needles."},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"citations":[{"type":"web_search_result_location","cited_text":"During RF microneedling, the needle tips emit radiofrequency waves that heat deep skin tissue layers. Radiowaves, a form of energy related to light an...","url":"https://bhskin.com/blog/guide-radiofrequency-microneedling-benefits-risks-tips/","title":"Radiofrequency Microneedling Guide: Process, Benefits & Tips","encrypted_ind