earch_result_location","cited_text":"Key BenefitsIt stimulates collagen production, reduces wrinkles, improves skin texture, and minimizes pores. ","url":"https://santeclinics.com/blog/radiofrequency-microneedling-differences","title":"RF Microneedling: Benefits and Differences Explained.","encrypted_index":"Eo8BCioIEBgCIiQ3ZWM1ZDE4ZC04YThiLTQ5OTItOTY1Zi05YWEwN2RhYThhY2ESDPklDxUwB4qYwMobPhoM4ZdAtDf/yL9+7vFYIjBT0EsgfeCJqdlmt5ex8c6fD4MAJCB12HHlH3ts5wKv1IPfXWbX8kBJUbdoVMTfAacqE0/iPiidg/eieMcvobuR7dKybjQYBA=="}],"type":"text","text":"It stimulates collagen production, reduces wrinkles, improves skin texture, and minimizes pores."},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"citations":[{"type":"web_search_result_location","cited_text":"This process selectively destroys abnormally formed collagen strands, softening scars. It also triggers inflammation and enhances collagen production,...","url":"https://bhskin.com/blog/guide-radiofrequency-microneedling-benefits-risks-tips/","title":"Radiofrequency Microneedling Guide: Process, Benefits & Tips","encrypted_index":"EpEBCioIEBgCIiQ3ZWM1ZDE4ZC04YThiLTQ5OTItOTY1Zi05YWEwN2RhYThhY2ESDNkc1ddurM2LJkQJjhoMgvhqhDFrNkP+VqWBIjDOE2741adi9LbEP831M1zPAxdfOG58isA66co+hkSTLm1jFtfMPChb36kQ/j823eoqFVsp9aU/NlayVyjHeAVcXK7QVTom9RgE"}],"type":"text","text":"This process selectively destroys abnormally formed collagen strands, softening scars. It also triggers inflammation and enhances collagen production, which together reduce scar prominence while making the skin smoother and firmer."},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"citations":[{"type":"web_search_result_location","cited_text":"Suitable for All Skin Types: Unlike laser treatments, RF energy is colorblind, meaning it is safe for use on all skin tones without the risk of hyperp...","url":"https://www.eyre-esthetics.com/post/what-is-rf-microneedling","title":"What Is RF Microneedling & Skin Benefits Explained","encrypted_index":"Eo8BCioIEBgCIiQ3ZWM1ZDE4ZC04YThiLTQ5OTItOTY1Zi05YWEwN2RhYThhY2ESDGlEXBPyzYsxKV