 well as skin laxity and hyperhidrosis. ","url":"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31280844/","title":"Radiofrequency Microneedling: Overview of Technology, Advantages, Differences in Devices, Studies, and Indications - PubMed","encrypted_index":"Eo8BCioIEBgCIiQ3ZWM1ZDE4ZC04YThiLTQ5OTItOTY1Zi05YWEwN2RhYThhY2ESDOTl1nbaMtxcS2FWVRoMxApAYK9/0e/SVfpiIjCjObRpdBrqA5cDG4Fsn7tqeZxBDLraoCATfGPvmYSa17nI8AhuSiDvX7fdgpDCtQQqE9JmA3NZTLi4MRZzpG+VtWgS+90YBA=="}],"type":"text","text":"RF microneedling has also been used to successfully treat skin laxity and hyperhidrosis (excessive sweating)."},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n---\n\n### Combination with PRP\n\n"},{"citations":[{"type":"web_search_result_location","cited_text":"This can target: ... You can also get radiofrequency microneedling with platelet-rich plasma (PRP). In this procedure, your provider draws blood from ...","url":"https://www.healthline.com/health/radiofrequency-microneedling","title":"Radiofrequency Microneedling: Procedure, Aftercare, Side Effects, Cost","encrypted_index":"EpMBCioIEBgCIiQ3ZWM1ZDE4ZC04YThiLTQ5OTItOTY1Zi05YWEwN2RhYThhY2ESDCxOB8KJD02/AqhApBoMsH0pHk7OT+XTJ3dNIjBB/qHi1tB5h+0XH6jSOKvy+6vSAxKMH8zjxzUI1PwRkIQHLB42OwLUzCdUTz/ZPs0qF4ANyuTwogxwJdiEFkop/ymz8g/xBPRDGAQ="}],"type":"text","text":"You can also get radiofrequency microneedling with platelet-rich plasma (PRP). In this procedure, your provider draws blood from your arm and uses a machine to separate the platelets. After a microneedling session, your provider injects or applies the platelets to the treated area. This may maximize the results of your treatment."},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n---\n\n### Safety\n\n"},{"citations":[{"type":"web_search_result_location","cited_text":"Compared with treatments like chemical peels and dermabrasion, radiofrequency microneedling is minimally invasive. ","url":"https://www.healthline.com/health/radiofrequency-microneedling","title":"Radiofrequency Microneedling: Procedure, Aftercare, Side Effects, Cost","encrypted_i